msgctxt "mn17:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Middle Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn17:0.2"
msgid "Vanapatthasutta "
msgstr "Jungle Thickets "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: nya1, sc1
msgctxt "mn17:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "mn17:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "mn17:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "mn17:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn17:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "mn17:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya2
msgctxt "mn17:2.1"
msgid "“vanapatthapariyāyaṃ vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you an exposition about jungle thickets. "

msgctxt "mn17:2.2"
msgid "taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasikarotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn17:2.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "mn17:2.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya3, pts-vp-pli1.105, sc2
msgctxt "mn17:3.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, take the case of a mendicant who lives close by a jungle thicket. "

msgctxt "mn17:3.2"
msgid "Tassa taṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharato anupaṭṭhitā ceva sati na upaṭṭhāti, asamāhitañca cittaṃ na samādhiyati, aparikkhīṇā ca āsavā na parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, ananuppattañca anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nānupāpuṇāti. "
msgstr "As they do so, their mindfulness does not become established, their mind does not become immersed in samādhi, their defilements do not come to an end, and they do not arrive at the supreme sanctuary. "

msgctxt "mn17:3.3"
msgid "Ye ca kho ime pabbajitena jīvitaparikkhārā samudānetabbā—cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā—te kasirena samudāgacchanti. "
msgstr "And the necessities of life that a renunciate requires—robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick—are hard to come by. "

msgctxt "mn17:3.4"
msgid "Tena, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "That mendicant should reflect: "

msgctxt "mn17:3.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imaṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharāmi, tassa me imaṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharato anupaṭṭhitā ceva sati na upaṭṭhāti, asamāhitañca cittaṃ na samādhiyati, aparikkhīṇā ca āsavā na parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, ananuppattañca anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nānupāpuṇāmi. "
msgstr "‘While living close by this jungle thicket, my mindfulness does not become established, my mind does not become immersed in samādhi, my defilements do not come to an end, and I do not arrive at the supreme sanctuary. "

msgctxt "mn17:3.6"
msgid "Ye ca kho ime pabbajitena jīvitaparikkhārā samudānetabbā—cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā—te kasirena samudāgacchantī’ti. "
msgstr "And the necessities of life that a renunciate requires—robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick—are hard to come by.’ "

msgctxt "mn17:3.7"
msgid "Tena, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā rattibhāgaṃ vā divasabhāgaṃ vā tamhā vanapatthā pakkamitabbaṃ, na vatthabbaṃ. "
msgstr "That mendicant should leave that jungle thicket that very time of night or day; they shouldn’t stay there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya4, sc3
msgctxt "mn17:4.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharati. "
msgstr "Take another case of a mendicant who lives close by a jungle thicket. "

msgctxt "mn17:4.2"
msgid "Tassa taṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharato anupaṭṭhitā ceva sati na upaṭṭhāti, asamāhitañca cittaṃ na samādhiyati, aparikkhīṇā ca āsavā na parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, ananuppattañca anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nānupāpuṇāti. "
msgstr "Their mindfulness does not become established … "

msgctxt "mn17:4.3"
msgid "Ye ca kho ime pabbajitena jīvitaparikkhārā samudānetabbā—cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā—te appakasirena samudāgacchanti. "
msgstr "But the necessities of life are easy to come by. "

msgctxt "mn17:4.4"
msgid "Tena, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "That mendicant should reflect: "

msgctxt "mn17:4.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ kho imaṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharāmi. Tassa me imaṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharato anupaṭṭhitā ceva sati na upaṭṭhāti asamāhitañca cittaṃ na samādhiyati, aparikkhīṇā ca āsavā na parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, ananuppattañca anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nānupāpuṇāmi. "
msgstr "‘While living close by this jungle thicket, my mindfulness does not become established … "

msgctxt "mn17:4.6"
msgid "Ye ca kho ime pabbajitena jīvitaparikkhārā samudānetabbā—cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā—te appakasirena samudāgacchanti. "
msgstr "But the necessities of life are easy to come by. "

msgctxt "mn17:4.7"
msgid "Na kho panāhaṃ cīvarahetu agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito na piṇḍapātahetu … pe … na senāsanahetu … pe … na gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārahetu agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito. "
msgstr "But I didn’t go forth from the lay life to homelessness for the sake of a robe, alms-food, lodgings, or medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "mn17:4.8"
msgid "Atha ca pana me imaṃ vanapatthaṃ upanissāya viharato anupaṭṭhitā ceva sati na upaṭṭhāti, asamāhitañca cittaṃ na samādhiyati, aparikkhīṇā ca āsavā na parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, ananuppattañca anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nānupāpuṇāmī’ti. "
msgstr "Moreover, while living close by this jungle thicket, my mindfulness does not become established …’ "

msgctxt "mn17:4.9"
msgid "Tena, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā saṅkhāpi tamhā vanapatthā pakkamitabbaṃ, na vatthabbaṃ. "
msgstr "After reflection, that mendicant should leave that jungle thicket; they shouldn’t stay there. "

